3. Engage & Ask Questions
Reply to my emails. Leave comments. Tell me what topics confuse you. Share your experiences (good and bad).
This publication exists to serve you. The more you engage, the better I can tailor content to your actual needs.
4. Stay Skeptical
I mean it. Don't trust blindly – even me. Verify everything. Question claims. Do your own research (DYOR), here we go again!
That's exactly the mindset I want to cultivate. Healthy skepticism is your best protection in crypto.
